name: Study Now
overview:
StudyNow provides a searchable database of courses that can be studied in Australia or from around the world. We believe there is no better way for potential students to find education and training.

Study Now gives students the chance to research and browse courses from a range of institutions in a range of locations and settings previously unknown to the candidate. Students can select from classroom courses, Online Courses and Correspondence Courses to name a few For institutions, StudyNow offers incredibly detailed profiles of candidates. This helps to make sure that institutions get exactly the right student.
